snippet.title: Getting Un-Stuck, Amber Cabral (Speaker, Writer, Consultant, and CEO)
snippet.description:
What possibility do you see yourself creating?

Amber is a speaker, writer, inclusion and diversity consultant, and CEO at Cabral CO. She is also a chair for Brown Girls do Ballet

"My possibility is to create a world that is inviting and safe for diverse people to showcase their talent." - Amber Cabral
